title: NMPreps.com's Top 50 Volleyball Players
text:
NMPreps.com's Top 50 Volleyball Players Joshua J. Grine NMPreps.com Basketball Analyst 
Today, NMPreps.com releases it's Top 50 volleyball players for the 2015 season. The state of New Mexico has a wealth of talent this season and with three players already committed to the next level we will try and highlight the 50 top players this season. NMPreps.com's Top 50 Volleyball Players 
No. 50 ROSE MOON Santa Fe Waldorf (Santa Fe, NM) | Freshman | 5-foot-8 | OH 
Notes: Moon, only a freshman that will graduate in 2019 is having a special season for a top team in her classification. With 228 kills (46.5%), 60 aces and 150 digs on the season it was hard to not take notice.. continue reading here 
No. 49 ELLIE BREEDEN St. Mike's (Santa Fe, NM) | Junior | 6-foot | MBâ€‹ 
Notes: Breeden, is quietly helping the Lady Horsemen this season into what should be a state tournament birth with great play down the stretch. Breeden has 66 kills and 133 (leads the state) blocks.. continue reading here
